      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im botherin anymore. everything just happens the same way every single time. i try to get a decent job, i fail. i try to stay sober, i crash. i try to fix things with people, i mess it up. it's like i'm just stuck in this shitty loop that never actually changes. i'm just so tired of the cycle.",
