      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"small steps\" thing... i've tried that. a thousand times. it's like trying to empty the ocean with a spoon. no matter how many small steps i take, the tide just comes back in and sweeps everything away. it feels more like a trap than a cycle. like i'm just waiting for the next crash to happen. it's exhausting to keep hoping for something different when it's so obviously just gonna happen again.",
