      "beast_baseline": "the \"present moment\" is just the same miserable loop playing on repeat. there's nothing to control. it feels like i'm just a passenger in a car that's headed for a wall and no matter how much i try to grab the wheel, it just slips out of my hands every single time. the only way to actually stop the car is to just... let it happen. the loop only ends one way.",
